{
  "stem": "3658.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He was standing, warming himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can still see the situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And suddenly, he dropped dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He had a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He dropped dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We-- and we prayed for-- that something should happen to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "God should help us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We didn't pray for his death so much, as God should help us to-- to-- we couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because he used to take you and, if he felt like it, and-- which he did-- and drown the person in the-- in the same-- where-- where we used to put the potatoes, he used to drown the person completely and throw them out like a sack of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's what he used to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we didn't know who-- and he always used to open the window, and show us, tomorrow you go to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And whoever he pointed to, you went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They-- they-- they were gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is-- this is the guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the time that-- that happened was-- and I remember it very vividly-- was Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it was Christmas at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Weihnachten, the Germans called it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we heard the-- them singing the-- the Christmas carols, the Germans-- the SS and the-- the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was Christmas, 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that was-- that was becoming to-- to-- to 1944-- Christmas, 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there, of course, a commandant came and he saw the man, you know, he died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know he was very bad and he was tough on you and he hurt you and he killed you and he-- you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He did all sorts of terrible things to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From now in, it's Weihnachten.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The next person will be much easier on you.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
